Package routerrental_package

Class SystemInformationPrinter

java.lang.Object
routerrental_package.SystemIformationHolder
routerrental_package.SystemInformationPrinter
class SystemInformationPrinter
extends SystemIformationHolder
System printer Class that prints any information needed by the system users [Admin/Customer]. All the functions apply Least Privilege principle.
